      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. It delivers exceptional throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity during spirited cornering. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. With its factory limited-slip differential and a linear power band that screams to an 8,000 RPM redline, this M3 offers an authentic analog performance experience.",
